urce=gbs_api"},"language":"en","previewLink":"http://books.google.com.eg/books?id=XQUdTobQExoC&printsec=frontcover&dq=sports&hl=&cd=2&source=gbs_api","infoLink":"http://books.google.com.eg/books?id=XQUdTobQExoC&dq=sports&hl=&source=gbs_api","canonicalVolumeLink":"https://books.google.com/books/about/Sports_Tourism.html?hl=&id=XQUdTobQExoC"},"saleInfo":{"country":"EG","saleability":"NOT_FOR_SALE","isEbook":false},"accessInfo":{"country":"EG","viewability":"PARTIAL","embeddable":true,"publicDomain":false,"textToSpeechPermission":"ALLOWED","epub":{"isAvailable":false},"pdf":{"isAvailable":true,"acsTokenLink":"http://books.google.com.eg/books/download/Sports_Tourism-sample-pdf.acsm?id=XQUdTobQExoC&format=pdf&output=acs4_fulfillment_token&dl_type=sample&source=gbs_api"},"webReaderLink":"http://play.google.com/books/reader?id=XQUdTobQExoC&hl=&source=gbs_api","accessViewStatus":"SAMPLE","quoteSharingAllowed":false},"searchInfo":{"textSnippet":"The authors present sports tourism as a unique area that produces its own issues, concerns and controversies. The study is based upon a set of international case studies and includes four extended and detailed case study chapters."}},{"kind":"books#volume","id":"PjSoDwAAQBAJ","etag":"PArXUUtkAOk","selfLink":"https://www.googleapis.com/books/v1/volumes/PjSoDwAAQBAJ","volumeInfo":{"title":"Methodology in Sports History","authors":["Wray Vamplew","Dave Day"],"publisher":"Routledge","publishedDate":"2018-12-07","description":"The process of converting the ‘past’ into ‘history’ involves engagement with a multitude of different sources and methods, and sports historians inevitably participate in the same debates over approaches and methodologies as their counterparts in other historical disciplines. At its heart, history remains a genre of empirical knowledge that is based upon the remains of the past, and without suitable evidence, there can be no sports history. A burgeoning range of sources has stimulated new ways of thinking and a significant expansion in the sports historian’s evidentiary base, as textual sources have been supplemented by photos, films and cartoons, uniforms, architecture, maps and landscapes, and material culture more generally. This book deals with some of these innovations. It is divided into two sections, the first offering chapter-length studies of particular methodologies, and the second, brief responses from experts in their fields to the question ‘what can sports historians learn from other disciplines?’","industryIdentifiers":[{"type":"ISBN_13","identifier":"9781351727709"},{"type":"ISBN_10","identifier":"1351727702"}],"readingModes":{"text":true,"image":true},"pageCount":433,"printType":"BOOK","categories":["Sports & Recreation"],"maturityRating":"NOT_MATURE","allowAnonLogging":false,"contentVersion":"1.1.1.0.preview.3","panelizationSummary":{"containsEpubBubbles":false,"containsImageBubbles":false},"imageLinks":{"smallThumbnail":"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=PjSoDwAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=5&edge=curl&source=gbs_api","thumbnail":"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=PjSoDwAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api"},"language":"en","previewLink":"http://books.google.com.eg/books?id=PjSoDwAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&dq=sports&hl=&cd=3&source=gbs_api","infoLink":"https://play.google.com/store/books/details?id=PjSoDwAAQBAJ&source=gbs_api","canonicalVolumeLink":"https://play.google.com/store/books/details?id=PjSoDwAAQBAJ"},"saleInfo":{"country":"EG","saleability":"FOR_SALE","isEbook":true,"listPrice":{"amount":1673.88,"currencyCode":"EGP"},"retailPrice":{"amount":1673.88,"currencyCode":"EGP"},"buyLink":"https://play.google.com/store/books/details?id=PjSoDwAAQBAJ&rdid=book-PjSoDwAAQBAJ&rdot=1&source=gbs_api","offers":[{"finskyOfferType":1,"listPrice":{"amountInMicros":1673880000,"currencyCode":"EGP"},"retailPrice":{"amountInMicros":1673880000,"currencyCode":"EGP"}}]},"accessInfo":{"country":"EG","viewability":"PARTIAL","embeddable":true,"publicDomain":false,"textToSpeechPermission":"ALLOWED","epub":{"isAvailable":true,"acsTokenLink":"http://books.google.com.eg/books/download/Methodology_in_Sports_History-sample-epub.acsm?id=PjSoDwAAQBAJ&format=epub&output=acs4_fulfillment_token&dl_type=sample&source=gbs_api"},"pdf":{"isAvailable":true,"acsTokenLink":"http://books.google.com.eg/books/download/Methodology_in_Sports_History-sample-pdf.acsm?id=PjSoDwAAQBAJ&format=pdf&output=acs4_fulfillment_token&dl_type=sample&source=gbs_api"},"webReaderLink":"http://play.google.com/books/reader?id=PjSoDwAAQBAJ&hl=&source=gbs_api","accessViewStatus":"SAMPLE","quoteSharingAllowed":false},"searchInfo":{"textSnippet":"This book deals with some of these innovations."}},{"kind":"books#volume","id":"pp6sDQAAQBAJ","etag":"qw62eNDPTKE","selfLink":"https://www.googleapis.com/books/v1/volumes/pp6sDQAAQBAJ","volumeInfo":{"title":"الصحافة الرياضية Sports Journalism","authors":["فيل أندروز"],"publisher":"Al Manhal","publishedDate":"2015-01-01","description":"لقد تطورت الصحافة الرياضية واتسعت بشكل سريع خلال السنوات القليلة الماضية، كما أنها تعد وسيلة تسويقية هامة بالنسبة للمؤسسات الإعلامية، وخاصة شبكات التلفزيون التي تعمل ببث الأقمار الصناعية والمواقع الإلكترونية. ويعد نقل الأحداث الرياضية واحدًا من الأدوار والمهام الرئيسية للصحفيين الرياضيين، حيث يتضمن هذا نطاقًا واسعًا من الأنشطة، بداية من العروض المسبقة ومقالات المعلومات الأساسية والتي تمهد المشهد للحدث، وحتى التقارير الفورية للأحداث، والمقالات الأكثر عمقًا وتفصيلًا، والمقالات التوضيحية التي يتم كتاباتها بعد إقامة الحدث. وتلعب المقالات الرياضية المتخصصة الكثير من الأدوار الهامة في الصحف والمجلات، فطولها يسمح للصحفيين بالتعمق في كتابة مواضيعهم وتمنحهم الفرصة لمعالجة المادة الخاصة بهم بطريقة ممتعة ومبتكرة، وبالتالي تمنع القراء التسلية والترفيه الذي يبحثون عنه في الصفحات الرياضية، كما أنها تمنح الفرصة لإبداء الرأي وللتحليل والتي عادة ما يتم استبعادها من القصص الإخبارية، ولكن كتابة المقالات تتطلب أيضًا بعض المهارات بنفس القدر الذي تتطلبه الكتابة عن الأحداث الرياضية أو كتابة القصص الإخبارية. ويدفع النمو السريع للصحافة الإلكترونية الصحفيين إلى ابتكار وتبني سلسلة جديدة من المهارات والأساليب لتلبية متطلبات الجمهور من الأخبار، والمعلومات، والتحليلات، والتعليقات الفورية أينما تحدث؛ فهذا يتضمن الأخبار العاجلة، والتغطية المباشرة للأحداث، والروابط المرئية والصوتية، والمدونات، والمقاطع الصوتية، والمحادثات عبر الإنترنت. فالأسلوب الصحفي يتكيف طبقًا للمتطلبات التكنولوجية التي تستخدم من خلالها، كما يتبنى الصحفيون خاصية التفاعلية التي تقدمها التكنولوجيا الرقمية، ولا سيما القدرة على دمج المعلومات وإبداء التعليقات من جانب جمهورهم.","industryIdentifiers":[{"type":"ISBN_13","identifier":"9796500178592"}],"readingModes":{"text":false,"image":true},"pageCount":303,"printType":"BOOK","categories":["Language Arts & Disciplines"],"maturityRating":"NOT_MATURE","allowAnonLogging":false,"contentVersion":"1.2.1.0.preview.1","panelizationSummary":{"containsEpubBubbles":false,"containsImageBubbles":false},"imageLinks":{"smallThumbnail":"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=pp6sDQAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=5&edge=curl&source=gbs_api","thumbnail":"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=pp6sDQAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api"},"language":"ar","previewLink":"http://books.google.com.eg/books?id=pp6sDQAAQBAJ&pg=PA52&dq=sports&hl=&cd=4&source=gbs_api","infoLink":"https://play.google.com/store/books/details?id=pp6sDQAAQBAJ&source=gbs_api","canonicalVolumeLink":"https://play.google.com/store/books/details?id=pp6sDQAAQBAJ"},"saleInfo":{"country":"EG","saleability":"FOR_SALE","isEbook":true,"listPrice":{"amount":485.65,"currencyCode":"EGP"},"retailPrice":{"amount":485.65,"currencyCode":"EGP"},"buyLink":"https://play.google.com/store/books/details?id=pp6sDQAAQBAJ&rdid=book-pp6sDQAAQBAJ&rdot=1&source=gbs_api","offers":[{"finskyOfferType":1,"listPrice":{"amountInMicros":485650000,"currencyCode":"EGP"},"retailPrice":{"amountInMicros":485650000,"currencyCode":"EGP"}}]},"accessInfo":{"country":"EG","viewability":"PARTIAL","embed